{"tid":1379177,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"希望每一個人要有一個心態","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:39:27.000Z","uid":10228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd313f4c96eeff0fe7be30dc32060a07fd1e053","tid":1379177,"uid":10228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"我哋依家係同緊一個暴力嘅政權打緊仗<br />\n喺每一次發夢入面 我自己由backup走到去前線<br />\n見過好多唔同既人 我好多謝好感激每一個人<br />\n到今日我都仲見到好多人湧到前面就係為左影張相打個卡 <br />\n係後面 我見到有人仲拎電話黎打機<br />\n屌 依家咩時勢呀 前線手足見到咁好心嗡<br />\n<br />\nBe water, formless, shapeless.<br />\n<br />\n水能載舟亦能覆舟<br />\n作為同伴 大家可唔可以醒小小<br />\n話比一班手足知 有一班堅決既後盾<br />\n知道後盾唔係淋既<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都攰 我可嘗唔係呢?<br />\n大家加油 對準暴力政權<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"10414bd4bae1da011c86522f3412611bc47e57f3","tid":1379177,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fe9df71ab8b8c1951bc067abd7662d8ebc7622f","tid":1379177,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"戰場唔係拍拖地方，認真<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防護裝備用完唔好亂掉，呢啲唔係武器，俾人搜到都唔怕。<br />\n俾人查身份證都驚就唔好學人講抗爭。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑警問點解帶防具出街，你就答：<br />\n<strong><ins>而家警察落閘唔出勤，市民戴保護裝備出街好合理！<br />\n警察盡責嘅話，我洗攞咁多重野出街食飯？！<br />\n呢啲係冇攻擊性嘅防護措施，唔通海邊嘅救生圈、船上嘅救生衣都犯法？</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>727有兩個情況嚴重，希望平安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n728少好多full gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><em>所以話防具好重要，尤其係保命嘅電單車頭盔，工地安全帽唔夠保護性！</em></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">電單車頭盔要買snell安全標準嘅，聽講可以擋到時速500公里嘅氣槍</span></ins></strong></span>，詳細睇：<a href=\"https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fultimatemotorcycling.com%2F2013%2F04%2F08%2Fmotorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=23f53005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372308</a>"},{"pid":"6e5b481ddee76db292af8e8e0decc05ffc006e98","tid":1379177,"uid":16124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}